  "text": "Work by Leino and Nelson [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , and Müller [CITATION_3] provides a sound and modular handling of model fields using different techniques. However, neither of the two approaches allows representation functions for model fields to include method calls, thus preventing the need of handling side-effects.",
